## CLI

Comandos principais:

```powershell
chronos generate-generalist
chronos generate-specialist
chronos train-generalist
chronos train-specialist
chronos simulate
chronos validate-apophis
```

Se `chronos` nao estiver no PATH:

```powershell
python -m chronos_safe.apps.cli.main <comando>
```

